metadata.name: FIGHT THE POWER
metadata.description:
Part of the METAPRIDE LAND 2022 Collection

Royal entered the NFT space and realized that their physical collection of work had thousands of other possibilities. Now using their Street style in a more unique way, Royal is reimagining fine art for the Digital age exploring the integration of physical and digital art. 

You can view their NFTs, Street Art and Fashion at www.royal.wtf or on twitter @GraffitiUrban
